extends layout

block content
    div(class="textBody")

        div(class="section")

            h1(class="heading large")   Staying in Albuquerque
            p(class="textBlock")
                | For our guests, we reccomend one of two options for your stay
                | in Albuquerque.  There are a limited number of rooms available
                | at Los Poblanos, and if you're interested you can check availability
                | by contacting them.  Second, we have blocked out rooms at the Sheraton
                | Albuquerque Uptown.  If you choose to stay at the Sheraton, we will
                | provide transport to and from the ceremony and reception for all of our
                | guests.

        div(class="section")

            h1(class="heading large")   Los Poblanos Organic Farm
            p(class="textBlock")
                | Our ceremony and reception will be held at Los Poblanos Organic Farm,
                | and Los Poblanos has a handful of rooms available for varying rates.
                | All of the rooms are luxurious, and include complementary gourmet breakfast and
                | full access to the grounds.  This is perfect if you're interested in
                | being surrounded by nature and want to feel separated from the city.
                | Los Poblanos will provide a calm and relaxing experience.  Rooms start at
                | $156 a night and go from there!

            p(class="textBlock")
                | If you would like more information about Los Poblanos, please visit their
                | Accommodations page <a href="http://www.lospoblanos.com/accommodations/" target="#">here.</a>
                | Please mention the Steiling-Woody wedding if you would like to book so we
                | know how many of our guests are staying there.

        div(class="section")
            h1(class="heading large")   Sheraton Albuquerque Uptown
            p(class="textBlock")
                | We have arranged for a block of rooms at the <a href="http://www.starwoodhotels.com/sheraton/property/overview/index.html?propertyID=713" target="#">Sheraton Albuquerque Uptown</a>.  This hotel is
                | located near an outdoor shopping mall and various restraunts and bars.
                | The hotel offers a complimentary shuttle that will take you to The Shops at ABQ Uptown.
                | If you would like to book, please visit the link below or call (505) 881-0000 and state that you are part of the Steiling-Woody
                | wedding to get a deal of $89.00 a night.

    script
        $(document).ready(function (){
            $('#accommodations').addClass('selected').removeClass('unselected');
        });